.TH "LIGHTNING-SEED" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-seed \- clightning hsm_secret export / import / verify
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning seed
[\fIsubcommand\fR] [\fIargs\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.nf
lightning seed — clightning hsm_secret export / import / verify.

Implements FEAT-185 §Seed.

Subcommands:
  export                  print the seed-derived mnemonic (read once)
  import                  initialise a fresh hsm_secret from a mnemonic
  verify                  prompt for 2 random words; pass/fail
.fi
.SH USAGE
.nf
usage: lightning seed <subcommand>

   export                 print the seed-derived mnemonic
   import                 initialise hsm_secret from a mnemonic
   verify                 prompt for 2 random words
.fi
.SH "SEE ALSO"
.BR lightning (1)
.SH AUTHOR
Part of the \fBlightning\fR educational Lightning Network frontend.
